==Personal life== Ghilas' younger brother, [[Nabil Ghilas|Nabil]], was also a footballer and a forward. He too played in France, Portugal and for Algeria.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.lebuteur.com/international/actualites/nabil-ghilas%C2%A0-%C2%A0-je-veux-faire-mieux-que-mon-frere|title=Nabil Ghilas : "Je veux faire mieux que mon frère"|trans-title=Nabil Ghilas : "I want to do better than my brother"|publisher=Le Buteur|language=French|date=28 August 2012|accessdate=16 December 2013|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218112334/http://www.lebuteur.com/international/actualites/nabil-ghilas%C2%A0-%C2%A0-je-veux-faire-mieux-que-mon-frere|archivedate=18 December 2013|df=dmy-all}}</ref>
